node.text: Ive never felt more confident, empowered and just all around cool. thank you to @si_swimsuit for including me in this years issue. all i want is for people to look at me and feel inspired that if I can accomplish what I have then you can too :)

node.text: Ive never felt more confident, empowered and just all around cool. thank you to @si_swimsuit for including me in this years issue. all i want is for people to look at me and feel inspired that if I can accomplish what I have then you can too :)
